# Summary
This documentation page describes how to integrate Amplitude with Segment to send behavioral cohorts from Amplitude to Segment, enabling businesses to use cohort data with ad networks, marketing tools, and personalization engines through Segment's platform. The integration works by sending user_id values with cohort membership flags as identify events.

